Name: Simulacrum Submersion
PeriodDesc: ['"Primo Sequence: Enemies come with radiation effects and deal damage to all characters. A character can deal 15% more Extra DMG for every 10s they stay on the battlefield, up to 225%, which will be cleared after they leave the battlefield."', 'Evolving Sequence: The enemy will generate a Shield after surviving for 15s.', '"End Sequence: When the enemy has no allies within 5m around them, they deal more damage and have higher DMG Reduction."', 'Loop Sequence: Killing enemies will make the character deal more damage for 5s.
